crp.c -> Chinese Restaurant Process.
irv.cpp -> Instant Runoff Voting. #not related to topic models
purn.cpp -> A simple C program to simualte polya's urn
stick.cpp -> A simple C program to simulate stick breaking process to generate dirichlet distribution.
gibbs3.py -> A simple python script where I have simuated some basic Gibbs sampling methods.
parliament_labels.py -> A simple python script where the uni-ngram analysis is done of the parliament documents from 1947-1949
